title: Elgin James, filmmaker/director
itunes:title: Elgin James, filmmaker/director
description:
Welcome to 2014 and I have some amazing episodes to bring you this year! The first of the year I wanted to bring you a chat I had with Elgin James who is an independent filmmaker (Little Birds) with a LARGE history within the independent music scene from playing in Righteous Jams & 454 Big Block as well as his ties with the notorious "crew" FSU. We discussed transformations, gang life and being a product of your surroundings.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
